00C8   20A9           00337    CALL    SEND_CMD                  
00C9   0008           00338    RETURN
                      00339     
                      00340 ;CLEAR_SCREEN:Fills all 84x6 = 504 bytes with 0x00, then resets cursor to top-left.                   
00CA                  00341 CLEAR_SCREEN:
